data.description: If you're looking for a quiet and established neighborhood to be a part of, then CHECK THIS HOME OUT. This 3 bedroom charmer has truly been taken care of and is ready for your personal touch. This is a truly rare find with solid wood cabinets and a great backyard. The windows and roof were both updated 3 years ago and there's a great shed out back that could be utilized in so many ways. The brick fireplace in the living area creates a warm and cozy centerpiece for many conversations to come. Call today for a private tour.
